      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Full length studio shot of five men in traditional clothes with military elements. All of them are wearing fur caps and they are carrying many weapons: swords, long rifles, guns, and bandoliers. Two of the men are lying on the floor and one is kneeling behind artificial rocks. The other two are standing. A painted canvas backdrop is creating the illusion of the scene being set in a park.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Title is a translation of the given by the Austrian Museum of Folk Life and Folk Art title in German: "Bulgarische Freiwillige im serbobulgarischen Krieg 1885."</ab>
